  "description": "You've made someone angry enough that they're now actively working against you.",
  "content": "It might have been something you said, something you did, a position you took, or simply being in someone's way. However it happened, you've acquired a new enemy. Someone who was neutral or maybe even friendly now actively opposes you. You can see it in how they look at you, how they talk about you when they think you can't hear, how they position themselves against your interests. The hostility is real and it's growing. Another name added to the list of people who want to see you fail.",
